snippet.title: Exoborne | Official Game Trailer | Into The Infinite 2024
snippet.description:
Embark on a high-stakes journey in Exoborne, a Tactical Open-world Extraction Shooter. Navigate an apocalyptic world, scavenging, crafting, and fighting to survive in a dynamic, hostile world. Developed by Sharkmob.

Sign up for future playtests: www.exoborne.com/
